Thanks to this course, I got a holistic perspective on the Gastrointestinal system, Reproductive system and Endocrine system Anatomically, Histologically and Embryologically.
Topics were presented in short videos and one after the other. Invaluable topic summaries were given at the end of the lesson, wonderful quizzes were administered.
I came out of the course better equipped than when I entered the course.
I would like to thank each of the three faculty members who contributed.
Murat Yagmurca, Bursa, Turkey
